snippet.textDisplay:
This line "may His favor be upon you, and a thousand generations " makes me imagine multitudes of sinners around the world—made known to them the great love of Almighty God through Jesus Christ, and received Him as their LORD and Savior

LORD, we praise for You are Holy,Holy, Holy
You create us, You are God Almighty who is in control of all things, and You are above all things, every knee will bow, every tongue will confess that You are King who shall reign forever more! And apart from You—Jesus there is no other savior

LORD help us with Your Holy Spirit to be salt and light in our family, community, campus, nation, and wherever we go around the world

Let Your Kingdom come, Your will be done! Amen!
